		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉朝空中发射一枚大冰雹，随后立即炸裂，裂成8根追踪冰刺，均造成<span color="#99ffff">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉立即使用炮筒发射2枚冰雹，均造成<span color="#99ffff">45%</span><span>伤害</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉驱使灵力，使炮筒凝聚寒气，并产生冰雾震，造成<span color="#99ffff">60%</span><span>伤害并进入强化状态：该状态下允许施放「沆霭眠凇」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="1012" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉的真本事之一。本技能有两种施放方式：<br/>1.低于<span color="#ffbfbf">80%</span><span>生命值时，莉琉升空，并借用2枚</span><span textDecoration="underline">坚石之晶</span><span>汲取力量，在场地内持续不断地降下冰晶，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害；<br/>2.低于</span><span color="#ffbfbf">15%</span><span>生命值时，莉琉爬上高塔吟唱，在场地内持续不断地降下冰晶，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉将炮筒滞空，命令其发射从天而降的冰锥，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
