			<content>
				<p textAlign="right" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：NA</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99e5ff" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="60" y="342" width="311" height="151" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">暝视龙武士·<br/>「伊奎米利的寒星」<br/><span fontSize="60">「莉琉」</span></p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#bfefff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="61" y="497" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="16" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="272" height="40" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="16" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">Iktomisaurus Warroir: <br/>Frost Star of Ixquimilli：Liliuo</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#bfefff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="67" y="976" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="442" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">坚岩之晶：4次次数盾，击破其中一个即可打断莉琉招式，并致摔伤。<br/>常驻抗打断0.25。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/莉琉.assets/Image_19.png')" x="64" y="78">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="437" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉拿着炮筒进行划、砸2段攻击，分别造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%,70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">莉琉拿着炮筒进行格挡，可格挡最多4次，满4次时立即触发闪现，并施放随机小技能。此后各有50%概率将格挡计数重置为1或0。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
